</li><li> Lord Stingray in <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/Superjail" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/Superjail">Superjail!</a></em> Possibly justified if he isn't human.
</li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MrBogus" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/MrBogus">Mr. Bogus</a></em> has one, in regards of <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigEater" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BigEater">when food is involved</a>.
</li><li> Tung from <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/DexHamiltonAlienEntomologist" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/DexHamiltonAlienEntomologist">Dex Hamilton: Alien Entomologist</a></em>, who has frog DNA. His tongue borders on being prehensile.
